Author: ccore.io
Title: [ANN] Ccore Exchange
Body: Ccore is a Crypto Payment Platform. It allows people who have cryptocoins/altcoins to spend them on various fiat based online services and stores without losing value on the exchange.  Ccore consist of 3 modules: Exchange, Wallet, Payment System.  At the moment we are developing a massive part of the project — Ccore Exchange — an exchange for trading of various cryptocurrencies. We launched the alpha version and currently working on a beta version. At the same time we are working on Ccore Wallet.  Ccore Website - ccore.io Ccore Exchange - ccore.io/exchange  Ccore Tokens is a digital currency which you can pay for goods or services in online stores, as well as get a 50% discount on commission when trading on the Ccore Exchange.  Ccore Token currently trades on: IDEX - https://idex.market/eth/cco FORKDELTA - https://forkdelta.github.io/#!/trade/CCO-ETH MERCATOX - https://mercatox.com/exchange/CCO/BTC ETHERDELTA - https://etherdelta.com/#CCO-ETH  We are working on listing in other exchanges.

Author: ccore.io
Title: [ANN] Ccore Exchange
Body: Ccore team work in February     Recently, the Ccore development team has been focused on the implementation of the technical part of the project. There were no news about us in social media since.  We assembled a marketing team for this purpose which continued active work on the PR of our project.  According to the official Roadmap, work proceeds on our new site ccore.pro, which will soon be transferred to the ccore.io domain.  In the 1 quarter 2018, we moved the planned work on Ccore Walet for the 2 quarter 2018.  At the moment we are developing a massive part of the project — Ccore Exchange — an exchange for trading of various cryptocurrencies. We launched the alpha version and currently working on a beta version.  Ccore Exchange Alfa Version  Work on Ccore Walet will be continued in the 2 quarter 2018.  We make everything to do the assigned work on the Roadmap was completed on the promised dates.  Many thanks to our subscribers and all the people who follow our activities.  Sincerely, Ccore team.

Author: cryptoofox
Title: [ANN] Ccore Exchange
Body: Hi ennas, we are currently listed on etherdelta and mercatox exchanges as follows  ✔️ $BTC Market ➖https://mercatox.com/exchange/CCO/BTC ✔️ $ETH Market ➖https://mercatox.com/exchange/CCO/ETH ✔️ Ether Delta ➖https://etherdelta.com/#CCO-ETH  We are in discussion with more exchanges at the moment, we will be updating you in coming weeks.

Author: cryptoofox
Title: [ANN] Ccore Exchange
Body: Main features can be listed as follows.  ✔ CCORE EXCHANGE (C-EXCHANGE) C-Exchange is a cryptocurrency exchange where cryptocurrency can be exchanged with each other or fiat currency. ✔ CCORE WALLET (C-WALLET) C-Wallet is a multi-currency wallet where funds of CCORE users are kept. ✔ CCORE PAY (C-PAY) C-Pay is a full payment system, which allows the merchants selling products and services against cryptocurrencies by integrating C-Pay on the web site of online-store.  Please check our whitepaper for more details.

Author: cryptoofox
Title: [ANN] Ccore Exchange
Body: Excellent question series, let me explain in this way.  Coinbase never allows people to do payment to a online portal/online retailer like ebay. However, CCORE is planning to achieve that. CCORE platform acts as the intermediary between FIAT value of the item and the crypto value of the item. At the end of the day, online retailers will receive the required FIAT currency whereas Consumers/customers can use their cryptoocurrncies to pay the item via ccore platform. Hope I answered your first question. Next, Yes we are looking to expand the range of ccore platform. We are planning to offer our product to online retailers giants like ebay and alibaba. There won't be any restriction to anybody, unless governments have any rules or regulation against it.

Author: cryptoofox
Title: [ANN] Ccore Exchange
Body: Yes the platform will be built for computers, tablets and mobiles separately. Our main focus right now is the main ccore platform development

Author: cryptoofox
Title: [ANN] Ccore Exchange
Body: Hi, We have collected around 3000ETH during presale and ICO. THe reason behind total supply reduction is that we wanted to show the crypto community that we are very serious about our project quality and our token quality. We could have easily gone with 100 million but we discussed among our project members and advisers. We really want to maintain the quality and price  of our token in a healthy position.

Author: cryptoofox
Title: [ANN] Ccore Exchange
Body: It's something we are extremely mindful of, we can rely on a fix rate as cryptocurency values change all the time. it's more volatile than FIAT currencies. First we will only allow the main crypto coins to come through our system. Later we will expand the range.

Author: cryptoofox
Title: [ANN] Ccore Exchange
Body: Hello, thank you for the question, I don't think there is any service which allows you to pay an online retailer using cryptocurrency. For instance, ebay is not letting you pay the goods using your crypto assets. That's what we are trying to solve. we will allow you to pay in crypto and letting online retailers to get it in FIAT terms basically. For more info please read our white paper  thanks

Author: cryptoofox
Title: [ANN] Ccore Exchange
Body: HOW WILL THE CCORE PLATFORM BE ABLE TO REVOLUTIONIZE THE ONLINE RETAILERS INDUSTRY? COMPREHENSIVE PROJECT REVIEW ON CCORE BY CRYPTOFOX  CRYPTO PAYMENT PLATFORM FOR ONLINE RETAILERS AND CONSUMERS As the usage of cryptocurrency is inclining drastically, real world applications tend to get the benefits of merging with blockchain tech. For instance, Giants in Power & Energy, supply chain management, banking, real states and many more industries are digging deep into the research mode in order to find a solution for enhancing the efficiency and reliability of existing model with blockchain tech. However, cryptocurrencies are still in it’s infant stages. I reckon that only less than 15% of world population is aware about the cryptocurrencies. But as the time goes on, rest of the world will catch up and have the common courtesy to embrace the cryptocurrencies and blockchain technology as it’s going to revolutionize the economy. THERE HAS TO BE A WAY OF BUYING A LAPTOP ONLINE BY USING CRYPTOCURRENCY Nowadays, one of the main burning questions among many crypto enthusiasts is that when the giants of online retailers industry such as Ebay , Alibaba or Amazon are going to integrate crypto-currency payment options to current payment options. This is a valid question. The reason is being it’s extremely easier to pay up using cryptocurrencies without going into so much trouble or wasting much time. Let’s take a scenario where a person is trying to buy an item using credit card. He/She needs to put all those details from card number to living address and wait for the bank confirmation as usually card payments have to be confirmed by relevant banks. On the other hand, payment with crypto is much easier as counting 1, 2, 3. Just scan the QR code and put the amount and send. Once the miner confirmation comes the payment will be processed. If you really think about it, usage of cryptocurrency is a much more easy, efficient, reliable and time saving way of payment. So now we have built the foundation why cryptocurrency integration is imperative for the online retailers. Then WHY THE HELL NOT? There are many reasons behind that. The major one being the government interventions. Most of the company do not want to put their whole operation under jeopardy by using cryptocurrency payment methods as many governments put a red flag on usage of cryptocurrency. WHY USE ROUND WHEELS WHEN SQUIRE WHEELS ALREADY EXIST RIGHT? ~GOVERNMENTS  This is where CCORE project comes into play. The idea is very simple, “to be the platform between cryptocurrencies payments and online retailers. WHAT IS CCORE? CCORE is a Crypto Payment Platform that allows people who are having cryptocurrency to spend on various fiat based online services and stores without losing value on the exchange. And the owners of online-stores will be able to accept cryptocurrency for payment, while not losing part of their profit due to variation of cryptocurrency rate. In the first glance into CCORE ICO, I honestly thought this was a cheap ICO without any future. The website was a mess, no proper profiles for developers, whitepaper was below average. However, I had an oppertunity to talk to the CEO Mr. Artak Navoyan. He explained me the vision and the plans he is having for the future developments of CCORE platform. It aroused my interest towards the platform. The project is based on Armenia/Russia. Developers are bit slow in the common language. It was extremely difficult to communicate with them. Nevertheless, after talking to Mr. Navoyan, I knew this is the real deal if they can build a kick ass CCORE platform. This has the potential to create chills in giants like Ebay, Alibaba owners’ spines. Furthermore, Having used advantages of the decentralized currency, CCORE platform offers favorable operating terms both to merchants and consumers, therewith increasing turnover share of cryptocurrencies in business. So, we can change perception of the crux of cryptocurrencies from the tool of speculation to full-value currency, by which payment both in Online-store for purchase of telephone and in restaurant for a cup of coffee can be made.  OVERVIEW OF CCORE CONCEPT WHAT ARE THE MAIN CHALLENGES IN ONLINE RETAILER INDUSTRY WHICH CCORE PROJECT IS TRYING TO ADDRESS? As of today the main problem is that cryptocurrencies can’t be equated with fiat currency. With a purpose to settle this problem let’s discuss the main functions of money: ✔ Circulation medium ✔ Means of hoarding ✔ Measure of value So, as of today cryptocurrencies don’t have all the above mentioned functions. High volatility in cryptocurrencies’ price doesn’t allow securing the measure of value and, all the more, to save this value. This is the main reason for rejection to accept cryptocurrency for payment of products and services by entrepreneurs. HOW DOES CCORE WORK TO MITIGATE THOSE ISSUES? Their goal is to create comfortable conditions for all the market participants for operation with cryptocurrencies, where high volatility in cryptocurrency price ceases to be a problem. Our team develops CCORE platform for settlement of existing problems. Interconnection of CCORE with merchants is described in clause 1.3 in detail, where due to extension of C-PAY operation with cryptocurrencies may be accepted as a source additional profit by a businessman, which, in its turn, will lead to the increased popularity of cryptocurrencies in business environment. In the end cryptocurrencies will be provided function “measure of value” and become full challengers to fiat currency. ROAD MAP Road map looks good and best things are yet to come.  ROADMAP OF THINGS TO COME BASIC STRUCTURE OF CCORE CCORE comprises with 3 main components as follows, ✔ CCORE EXCHANGE (C-EXCHANGE) C-Exchange is a cryptocurrency exchange where cryptocurrency can be exchanged with each other or fiat currency. ✔ CCORE WALLET (C-WALLET) C-Wallet is a multi-currency wallet where funds of CCORE users are kept. ✔ CCORE PAY (C-PAY) C-Pay is a full payment system, which allows the merchants selling products and services against cryptocurrencies by integrating C-Pay on the web site of online-store.  MAIN SECTIONS OF CCORE PLATFORM PROTOTYPE VERSION AVAILABILITY Mr. Navoyan stated that the working product will be available by first quarter of 2018. The major issue they are facing at the moment is the financial terms. Once the ICO is done and dusted, They will go full throttle to deliver the outputs according the the time plan. However, members can get an idea about “How the platform will look like” by interacting the DEMO version they have provided. ✔ DEMO CCORE EXCHANGE is under construction ✔ DEMO CCORE WALLET➖Click Here ✔ DEMO CCORE PAY➖Click Here ECO SYSTEM They need to put the baby steps before catching the big guns. There is a ver very long way to go before even thinking about offering the product to giants like Ebay. As Mr. Navoyan pointed out, they are in discussion with few medium scale online retailers around the globe for testing our platform and might add those companies as a part of their ECO system. DEVELOPMENT TEAM Even though the language is a barrier for them. The team consists with top quality core development programmers with wealth of experience. ✔ CCORE TEAM➖Click Here CCORE PROJECT SUMMERY IN DETAIL 🔥CCORE SOCIAL COMMUNITY🔥 ✔ Website ➖ https://ccore.azureedge.net ✔ Telegram Troll-Box ➖ https://t.me/ccore_io ✔ Telegram Channel ➖ https://t.me/ccore_news ✔ Facebook ➖ https://www.facebook.com/ccore.io ✔ Twitter ➖ https://twitter.com/ccore_io ✔ Reddit ➖ https://www.reddit.com/user/ccore_io ✔ Bitcoin Talk ➖ https://bitcointalk.org/index.php?topic=2100088.0 ✔ Email ➖ info@ccore.io 🔥CCORE ICO DETAILS🔥 ✔ Starting Date➖09 November 2017 ✔ Ending Date➖30 November 2017 ✔ Ticker➖CCO ✔ Total CCOIN Supply➖10 000 000 CCO (Initial Total Supply was 100 million will be reduced to 10 million after burning/locking away 90 million CCO tokens) ✔ CCOIN tokens for Sale➖6 000 000 CCO ✔ Token exchange Rate➖1 ETH : 1000 CCO ✔ Currency Accepted➖ETH ✔ Minimum Transaction➖0.1 ETH 🔥BONUS STRUCTURE🔥 ✔ First Week➖1 ETH = 1200 CCO (20% Bonus) ✔ More than 10 ETH Transactions➖1 ETH = 1500 CCO (50% Bonus) BOUNTY CAMPAIGN  Currently, the bounty program is running successfully. Over 500 members are following and completing bounty related tasks. 1000 ETH worth bounty tokens to be distributed. ✔ Bounty Thread Click Here GIVEAWAY CAMPAIGN  The giveaway has been arranged as a part of viral marketing campaign to boost up the community awareness about CCORE project. ✔ Giveaway Form Click Here ✔ Giveaway Response Sheet Click Here ✔ Giveaway Announcement Click Here CCO TOKEN BURNING EVENT  In initial stages, it was decided to use the total supply as 100 000 000 CCO. However, the team later decided to burn/lock away 90% of the total supply (90 000 000 CCO) in order to maintain the quality of the token as well as the project ( 90% comprised with all the unsold tokens and a portion of allocated tokens for project development) It shows that the cooperate greed is not there unlike hyped garbage ICOs. Hence, the total supply will be reduced to 10 000 000 CCO tokens which allows CCO token to blossom with the project progress. The options are as follows ✔ By creating a contract which immediately self destructs and sends to its own address, or just send to his deployed implementation of it (Burning function has to be implemented when deploying the smart contract) ✔ The easiest way to lock away tokens peremenantly is to send tokens to the address 0x0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 One of the above mentioned methods will be used for CCO burning process. More details will follow… MISCELLANEOUS ITEMS OFFERED BY CCORE As a part of the marketing campaign. CCORE community has been offered a chance to collect a free casual T-shirt from the company. Please check the social media groups for more details. Author: prizes
Title: [ANN] Ccore Exchange
Body: Mike integrates Ccore Payment Service into his online store. The payment system of  Ccore calculates the value of the product for the selected cryptocurrency (Ccore  tokens, BTC, ETH, and all other altcoins) at the rate of Ccore Exchange. Thus, John gets  the possibility to buy product directly against the cryptocurrency price value. After the  payment of cryptocurrency enters into the Ccore Exchange, it instantly automatically  exchanges to fiat currency which is later transfered to Mike's account  in Ccore Wallet.  By choosing Ccore, Mike business is able to accept cryptocurrencies for payment  without a risking price changes in the rate of cryptocurrency used. John also benefits by  using Ccore to make purchases as he instantly avoids exchange fees, Bank fees and  payment processing fees, which are rendered unnecessary.   this point is paying product into online store without bank fees...great idea...hopefully suceed

Author: Vladdirescu87
Title: [ANN] Ccore Exchange
Body: Ccore Platform, Crypto Retail Becomes Reality  E-commerce is a vital part of any business. With the introduction of online payment platforms, there is no denying that shopping and other online transactions have become much easier. An example of a revolutionary discovery is Paypal.  PayPal is a real find for online shoppers, who are hunting for bargains days and nights. There is no limit to what Paypal can be used to purchase. The time is so limited today and shopping in malls takes so much efforts and even money. According to research by experts, in 2015, Paypal achieved 188 million users, 15,800 employees and almost 5 billion payments, $1.22 billion of company’s profit which shows its high level of acceptability.  However, Paypal is restricted to just fiat currencies used around the world. Cryptocurrencies are fast gaining grounds and deserve a platform that will enable its users have an even easier online experience similar to the use of Paypal. The need for this solution has birthed the innovative cryptopayment platform referred to as Ccore Platform.  What is Ccore Platform?  Ccore is a Crypto Payment Platform that allows those who have cryptocoins / altcoins to spend them on various fiat based online services and stores without losing value on the exchange. This simply means that there is no need to worry about converting bitcoins to fiat currency before making payments on online stores. Owners of online stores will be able to accept cryptocurrency for payment, while not losing part of their profit due to variation of cryptocurrency rate.  https://coinidol.com/ccore-platform-crypto-retail-becomes-reality/
